videos.headline: Brown breaks tackles on way to 93-yard TD
videos.description: Barry Brown breaks multiple tackles and  takes the Georgia St. kickoff 93 yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Gentry breaks off 69-yard TD
videos.description: Devin Gentry takes the crossing route 69 yards up the field for a Georgia St. touchdown.

videos.headline: Hart makes 1-handed TD grab
videos.description: Penny Hart reels in Conner Manning's pass with one hand and runs it in for a 50-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Louis sacks Manning
videos.description: Conner Manning is sacked by Donald Louis Jr. for a loss of 5 yards.

videos.headline: Gentry takes reverse for TD
videos.description: Devin Gentry extends Georgia State's lead with a 15-yard touchdown run on a reverse play.

videos.headline: Hart grabs another TD
videos.description: Penny Hart pulls in his second touchdown of the game, a 25-yard score.

videos.headline: Green goes off for 80-yard TD
videos.description: Marcus Green takes the Garrett Smith pass 80 yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Hart makes it a hat trick
videos.description: Penny Hart makes his third touchdown catch of the game on a 22-yard pass from Conner Manning.

videos.headline: Neal pounds in 1-yard TD
videos.description: Kyler Neal punches in a touchdown at the goal line.

videos.headline: Smith hits Hodoh for TD
videos.description: Jonathan Hodoh catches a 14-yard touchdown from Garrett Smith.

videos.headline: Smith tosses 12-yard TD
videos.description: Xavier Brown grabs a 12-yard touchdown from Garrett Smith late in the fourth quarter.
